# Sean C Foley


[**View Profile**](https://github.com/seancfoley)

Projects

* [Japt](https://seancfoley.github.io/Japt-Bytecode-Optimizer-for-Java/) - Bytecode optimization tool written in Java to ease development and deployment of Java
* [IPAddress](https://seancfoley.github.io/IPAddress/) - Java library for handling IP addresses, both IPv4 and IPv6
* [MJVMK](https://seancfoley.github.io/mjvmk/) - The Micro Java Virtual Machine Kernel is a portable preemptive real-time kernel with an integrated CLDC Java virtual machine designed for embedded systems.  Written in C, x86 assembly code, and Java.
* [Functional Doclet for Javadoc](https://github.com/seancfoley/Functional-Doclet-for-Javadoc) - produces Javadoc with a more functional perspective
* [High Performance C++ Queues](https://github.com/seancfoley/High-Performance-CPP-Queues) - High performance C++ implementation of producer/consumer queue architecture
